<media id="fs-id1165038304550" alt="Figure a shows a baby in a basket, with arrow T1 pointing up and arrow w pointing down. Figure b shows a free body diagram of arrow T1 pointing down. Figure c shows a free body diagram of T1 pointing down, T2 pointing up and mg pointing down.">
